products.ingredients_text: MILK CHOCOLATE (47%). INGREDIENTS: SUGAR, COCOA BUTTER, SKIMMED MILK POWDER (FROM COW), COCOA MASS, WHEY POWDER (FROM MILK), MILK FAT, *EMULSIFIER (SOYA LECITHIN), HAZELNUT PASTE, *ARTIFICIAL VANILLIN FLAVOUR. MILK CHOCOLATE CONTAINS: COCOA SOLIDS 25% MINIMUM. VANILLA FLAVOURED FILLING (41%). INGREDIENTS: NON-HYDROGENATED VEGETABLE OIL (PALM FRUIT), SUGAR, WHEY PERMEATE (FROM MILK), FULL CREAM MILK POWDER (FROM COW), *EMULSIFIER (SOYA LECITHIN), *ARTIFICIAL VANILLIN FLAVOUR. COCOA BISCUIT PIECES (12%). INGREDIENTS: WHEAT FLOUR (GLUTEN), SUGAR, NON-HYDROGENATED VEGETABLE OIL (PALM FRUIT), FAT REDUCED COCOA POWDER, GLUCOSE SYRUP, *RAISING AGENTS (SODIUM BICARBONATE, AMMONIUM BICARBONATE), SALT, *EMULSIFIER (SOYA LECITHIN), *ARTIFICIAL VANILLIN FLAVOUR. *REFERS TO FOOD GRADE ADDITIVE. CONTAINS: MILK, HAZENUT, WHEAT (GLUTEN), SOYA. MAY CONTAIN: OTHER NUTS
